Note on bundled data
--------------------

The list data under `data/lists/*` is sourced from two places:

  1. The upstream Lists project (https://github.com/listsfordesign/Lists),
     fetched at build time. The upstream repository does not include an
     explicit LICENSE file; the project README states the data is "ready
     to populate your mockups" and the site historically served the data
     publicly for the same purpose. We redistribute the data with
     attribution in good faith for the original intent (designer mockups
     and prototypes). If you are the upstream maintainer and wish us to
     change anything, please open an issue.

  2. Local additions in this repository — released under the MIT terms
     above.

Brand names, place names, and proper nouns appearing in the lists are the
property of their respective owners. Their inclusion as sample data does
not imply endorsement and is intended only as realistic-looking
placeholder content.
